      "id": "PopularPost206360",
      "post_content": "ion1000  \n  \n[Red Elemental Blast](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Red Elemental Blast)?  \nThat's a thematically important card that doesn't go into a very narrow and specific deck?  \n  \nPointless, annoying, narrow, and generally unpleasant cards have been printed literally in every set ever released. Don't pretend this is a new development.  \n  \nThat said, Magic was good, and remains good to this day. Go play something else. OR, go play with the piles of ancient cards you adore so much.",
